REMOVE Imper IF ((-1 NP-HEAD) OR (1 NP-HEAD));

REMOVE Fin IF (0 Sg1) (NOT -1* Subj + Sg1 BARRIER CLB) (NOT 1* Subj + Sg1 BARRIER CLB);
